  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect your ship against wave after wave of brightly coloured enemies in this fast paced arcade inspired shooter. Use your abilities to survive as long as you can!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Levelling system that unlocks abilities and game modes as you level up.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several abilities on cooldowns that help you fight the enemy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Addicting gameplay that you can't put down.    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You can use a controller or mouse and keyboard.      </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Local Leaderboard.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
